➜文章新恋情疑曝光，深夜崩溃大哭，美女全程陪伴擦泪
http://www.sohu.com/a/419463614_100091227	24576
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>今天，是吐槽渣男的吃瓜阿美。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">他又出事儿了？</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">最近，<strong>文章被拍到和陌生女子一起现身工作室的照片，</strong>俩人还一起吃了宵夜，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200919/5fa3e1f77ab84604ab7d63a3bde9aa83.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">被拍的女子帮文章擦眼泪，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200919/00476c25224d48b1a4c78c605b52c622.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">帮他重新戴好帽子，看上去还挺贴心的，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200919/d4cf69412b1f401baccc231d72f9e1ce.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
